A vast server room with towering black monolithic storage units, rendered in a vintage 1970s technical illustration style with muted oranges, browns, and creams. In the foreground, one massive storage cabinet is crumbling and fragmenting into geometric shards that float away like autumn leaves. Behind it, a sleek, compact crystalline structure glows with an inner amber light, representing efficient compression. The scene has the aesthetic of old technical manuals and patent drawings, with subtle cross-hatching and aged paper texture throughout. Dramatic spotlighting creates long shadows across a grid-patterned floor.
